Summary: Digital pic taken from moving car= teardrop shape over power lines & that night about 40 miles away 2nd pic of possible same object.
divs: sighting detailsjune 23, 2011 -while visiting relatives in nashville, tn, we went to the parthenon replica in centennial park. after leaving the parthenon, i shot a digital photo from the passenger's seat. i did not notice anything unusual until i looked at the photo on my laptop. to the right, over the power lines, there is a grayish\blackish teardrop shaped object, that fades out on one end. that same night, about 40 miles away, in portland, tn, i was shooting digital photos outside, at night. (i had been taking photos every night, trying to capture anything paranormal, as the area has a lot of civil war history. incidentally, i did get a lot of orbs on camera and possibly 2 apparitions, as well as a video of a chair moving, inside the octagon hall civil war museum.) anyway, again i didn't notice anything unusual with my eyes. when i looked at the photos on the laptop, i saw an object that could possibly be the same object photographed earlier, from a different angle. i am uploading both photos and am very interested in what you think they could be. thanks.
